{"tid":1075770,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人都用緊人工智能換算法(AI)外匯交易程式","createTime":"2019-03-24T11:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T05:17:36.000Z","uid":244020,"like":4,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c71ed2cc7cc5222457494a9334148df6595abcc2","tid":1075770,"uid":244020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"Hamilton or Benjamin <br />\n唔知大家有無聽過呢個ai software<br />\n小弟經朋友介紹下接觸呢個software<br />\n係試過demo既情況下，小弟都入左金試，so far一星期賺左接近USD70，感覺唔錯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAqkCxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAqkCxU.png&h=af6ce987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他用呢個software既用家都有幾好既result，有啲朋友仔賺成三百幾美金一個月，個個人既result都唔一樣，但暫時眼見都係每個星期都有賺。(以下係其他人result) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGbjS61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGbjS61.png&h=62a4ea05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCC3Akn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCC3Akn.png&h=ead49d62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtCWaTK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtCWaTK.png&h=7f90f34e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8c0TXyL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8c0TXyL.png&h=572aace6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係hamilton既result <br />\nBenjamin 就係本金大，風險大回報高啲既版本。<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺: 作為一個唔太熟投資或者懶既人但又想投資既人，呢個software係幾好用。之前試過投資股票，但都蝕哂，所以好怕投資。Hamilton 就相對低風險，回報穩定。最好既係，佢地係有group，有專人每個星期都會同你講較咩setting, 幾時on，幾時off trade，有任何conference，news會影響個市場，就會有提醒。唔洗冒因爲無時間miss out左要留意新聞既風險。<br />\nSetting都只係㩒幾個制就可以。<br />\n另外亦都有group係專門解答疑問，所有有唔明，有渠道可以問清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人都用緊，可以一齊研究研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果各位有興趣都可以pm我，我可以加大家入佢嗰個facebook private group，比大家了解下，睇下人地既result<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者有其他問題都可以一齊研究<br />\n<br />\n都要提提大家以下係過去既成績，並不代表將來既result，每個人result唔同，投資有一定既風險架。"},{"pid":"96c77c50c855f018ea48a37d50e755d4de1cb0c6","tid":1075770,"uid":22362,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪呢期賺夠<br />\n諗住俾人賺下"},{"pid":"26efd8f3b0673ccc512846add3a3d13cd06228d1","tid":1075770,"uid":244020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c77c50c855f018ea48a37d50e755d4de1cb0c6","tid":1075770,"uid":22362,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:29:25.000Z","msg":"巴打係咪呢期賺夠<br />\n諗住俾人賺下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:31:10.000Z","msg":"我都係用左一星期咋 想睇下有無人有玩或者一齊玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac6cdf80fe1f936b80e43ad99925ec0b97a4909","tid":1075770,"uid":31238,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"有興趣想瞭解多d ai trade fx<br />\n但樓主勁打手feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f738e53f430c958a4f710f2a74bc8ed10cdc384","tid":1075770,"uid":244020,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"3ac6cdf80fe1f936b80e43ad99925ec0b97a4909","tid":1075770,"uid":31238,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:39:07.000Z","msg":"有興趣想瞭解多d ai trade fx<br />\n但樓主勁打手feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:43:55.000Z","msg":"竟然係咁 ~ <br />\n小弟我身邊無乜人玩呢啲 唯有上黎搵朋友研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChing有聽過？"},{"pid":"b30e4cd1fd72319c548f914d748bfbc1a8a7ad76","tid":1075770,"uid":68944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"點收費"},{"pid":"6222c35423b068a1f42c779d62a4974e132e1d4a","tid":1075770,"uid":71738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"96c77c50c855f018ea48a37d50e755d4de1cb0c6","tid":1075770,"uid":22362,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":2,"rep