id":242348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be7dd7e89d2329b4b030de871b135b7cb58fc9b0","tid":1075770,"uid":244020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02027671f1441f0df60b2aec7957fb3aa8ad1cb6","tid":1075770,"uid":137493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"非農有機會爆倉，我試過過百種mql5入面個啲EA，0.01,0.02咁上無幾隻會唔爆倉，通常叫你用大資金慢慢賺少少個啲就係增加唔爆倉既機率，如果真係賺到錢，我諗應該會更加貴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T03:00:07.000Z","msg":"非農姐係咩？<br />\n平時既外匯投資係點買法？<br />\n可唔可以分享多少少<br />\n小弟有啲擔心添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"非農就業數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c0135ff4b30d3d206b1cb0e9623a9bb4cacab7","tid":1075770,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:42:12.000Z","msg":"好像很厲害"},{"pid":"aa3f097d1f5fca3f1b8ca7b33a2c2f9a3d6367cd","tid":1075770,"uid":242348,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c71ed2cc7cc5222457494a9334148df6595abcc2","tid":1075770,"uid":244020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T11:18:14.000Z","msg":"Hamilton or Benjamin <br />\n唔知大家有無聽過呢個ai software<br />\n小弟經朋友介紹下接觸呢個software<br />\n係試過demo既情況下，小弟都入左金試，so far一星期賺左接近USD70，感覺唔錯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAqkCxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAqkCxU.png&h=af6ce987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他用呢個software既用家都有幾好既result，有啲朋友仔賺成三百幾美金一個月，個個人既result都唔一樣，但暫時眼見都係每個星期都有賺。(以下係其他人result) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QGbjS61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQGbjS61.png&h=62a4ea05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jCC3Akn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjCC3Akn.png&h=ead49d62&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jtCWaTK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjtCWaTK.png&h=7f90f34e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8c0TXyL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8c0TXyL.png&h=572aace6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上都係hamilton既result <br />\nBenjamin 就係本金大，風險大回報高啲既版本。<br />\n<br />\n個人感覺: 作為一個唔太熟投資或者懶既人但又想投資既人，呢個software係幾好用。之前試過投資股票，但都蝕哂，所以好怕投資。Hamilton 就相對低風險，回報穩定。最好既係，佢地係有group，有專人每個星期都會同你講較咩setting, 幾時on，幾時off trade，有任何conference，news會影響個市場，就會有提醒。唔洗冒因爲無時間miss out左要留意新聞既風險。<br />\nSetting都只係㩒幾個制就可以。<br />\n另外亦都有group係專門解答疑問，所有有唔明，有渠道可以問清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人都用緊，可以一齊研究研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果各位有興趣都可以pm我，我可以加大家入佢嗰個facebook private group，比大家了解下，睇下人地既result<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者有其他問題都可以一齊研究<br />\n<br />\n都要提提大家以下係過去既成績，並不代表將來既result，每個人result唔同，投資有一定既風險架。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:42:17.000Z","msg":"留個tg ? 交流下setting  我唔用default幾好成績"},{"pid":"e0406ddfea447cd46a30db75419fb430a16c650a","tid":1075770,"uid":202122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"買住十個先"},{"pid":"dd24271d8de143c2a8785f64c0cb860dc51fe86e","tid":1075770,"uid":242348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0406ddfea447cd46a30db75419fb430a16c650a","tid":1075770,"uid":202122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:55:02.000Z","msg":"買住十個先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"一個咪夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠"},{"pid":"dd85000ffe16502033cbd376592d435f1bff4bbb","tid":1075770,"uid":244020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d1e88ed59a8e9779b3f335a3c1ea16749197c96","tid":1075770,"uid":242348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"自己友 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26